25号 这里是64号
25, this is 64. Over.

701
00:56:48,580 --> 00:56:49,950
这里是25号
This is 25. Over.

702
00:56:50,580 --> 00:56:53,850
25号 第四小队最靠近坠机地点
25, Chalk Four is closest to the crash site. Over.

703
00:56:54,050 --> 00:56:56,540
64号 我看不到坠机地点
64, I can't see the crash site. Over.

704
00:56:57,320 --> 00:56:59,990
25号 就在你的正东方 你能找到的
25, it's due east of you. You will find it.

705
00:57:00,230 --> 00:57:01,780
留下一些人继续防守
Leave a security element in place.

706
00:57:01,860 --> 00:57:04,090
带其他人赶往坠机地点
Take the rest of your chalk on foot to the crash.

707
00:57:04,160 --> 00:57:07,530
搜救生还者 守卫那一区 其它小队会过去会合的
Check for survivors. Secure the area. All other chalks will follow. Over.

708
00:57:10,200 --> 00:57:11,690
25号 你听到吗
25, do you read me? Over.

709
00:57:11,770 --> 00:57:12,860
收到
Roger that.

710
00:57:12,940 --> 00:57:14,840
杰利顿 施密德
Galentine! Schmid!

711
00:57:15,310 --> 00:57:16,540
去找尤瑞克
Go get Yurek.

712
00:57:16,610 --> 00:57:17,870
去找汤布里
Get Twombly.

713
00:57:18,340 --> 00:57:20,640
有一架黑鹰坠毁了
Hey, there's a Black Hawk down.

714
00:57:20,810 --> 00:57:22,680
汤布里和尼尔森留守
Twombly, Nelson, you're gonna stay here.

715
00:57:22,750 --> 00:57:25,780
你们守在这个街角 然后跟悍马车队一起撤离
You're gonna hold this corner and then exfil with the humvees.

716
00:57:25,850 --> 00:57:29,310
杰利顿 施密德 你们跟我一起走 都明白了吗 出发
Galentine, Schmid, you're coming with me. All right? Let's go.

717
00:57:30,460 --> 00:57:32,360
为什么要我留守
How come I got to stay back here?

718
00:57:32,430 --> 00:57:33,820
因为你很可靠
Because you're dependable.

719
00:57:35,130 --> 00:57:36,530
好吧
All right...

720
00:57:38,200 --> 00:57:39,460
出发
let's go!

721
00:57:44,770 --> 00:57:46,670
我恨我自己可靠
I hate being dependable, man.

722
00:58:01,250 --> 00:58:04,780
J25号 你的西面有敌人与你们并行前进
Juliet 25, hostiles advancing, parallel west to your position.

723
00:58:04,860 --> 00:58:07,020
有妇女儿童混在其中
Be advised, women and children among them. Over.

724
00:58:07,090 --> 00:58:08,560
靠着墙走
Hit the wall.

725
00:58:24,580 --> 00:58:26,480
敌袭
Incoming!

726
00:58:32,150 --> 00:58:33,380
手榴弹
Grenade!

727
00:58:49,600 --> 00:58:50,630
走
Go.

728
00:59:01,780 --> 00:59:03,910
还有人在里面
We still got guys inside!

729
00:59:03,980 --> 00:59:05,790
赶快 我还要赶去坠机地点
All right, all right, I'm gonna go to the crash.

730
00:59:05,820 --> 00:59:09,350
你带其他人去 我继续装载犯人
You take the rest of the team. I'll finish loading the prisoners.

731
00:59:09,420 --> 00:59:12,220
不 我们要一起去坠机地点
Negative! We're gonna proceed to the crash site together.

732
00:59:12,290 --> 00:59:14,520
守住防线 然后等悍马车队来 对吗 长官
Secure the perimeter, wait for the humvees. Right, sir?

733
00:59:14,590 --> 00:59:16,430
- 收到 - 跟我上
- Roger that. - Follow my lead.

734
00:59:17,000 --> 00:59:19,090
军士 听到吗
Sarg'nt, are you receiving me?

735
00:59:19,170 --> 00:59:21,830
听到了 我们马上走
Yeah, I heard you. We should be leaving soon.

736
00:59:23,700 --> 00:59:26,500
好了 我们要赶快行动
All right, we need to move out now!

737
00:59:26,570 --> 00:59:29,800
等犯人装完了我就去坠机地点接你们
I'll finish loading the prisoners and pick you up at the crash site!

738
00:59:29,880 --> 00:59:31,100
出发吧
Let's move out!

739
00:59:31,180 --> 00:59:32,700
出发了 快走
Moving out! Go!

740
00:59:39,720 --> 00:59:41,690
快上车 快上车
Get in! Get in!

741
00:59:41,890 --> 00:59:43,150
快点
Move!

742
00:59:56,600 --> 00:59:58,130
八点钟方向
Eight o'clock!

743
01:00:11,990 --> 01:00:14,280
格里姆斯 别靠着墙
Hey, Grimes, stay away from the walls.

744
01:00:29,340 --> 01:00:31,670
喂 格里姆斯 你没事吧
Hey, Grimes. You okay?

745
01:00:32,010 --> 01:00:33,270
没事
Yeah!

746
01:00:35,340 --> 01:00:36,710
走吧 马多克斯
Let's go, Maddox.

747
01:00:37,180 --> 01:00:39,700
- C-2 车队出发了 - 收到
- C-2, convoy's moving out. - Roger that.

748
01:00:39,780 --> 01:00:42,410
马多克斯 看看这些猪头 这些白痴
Maddox, look at these jerks! These idiots!

749
01:00:42,550 --> 01:00:44,740
快 转右 马多克斯 转右
Go, go! Right, Maddox, right!

750
01:00:54,690 --> 01:00:57,190
汤布里 车队走了
Twombly, the convoy is leaving!

751
01:00:57,460 --> 01:00:58,950
嘿 汤布里
Hey, Twombly!

752
01:01:00,200 --> 01:01:01,200
什么
What?

753
01:01:01,270 --> 01:01:03,460
- 我想他们肯定忘了我们 - 什么
- I think they've forgotten us. - What?

754
01:01:04,200 --> 01:01:05,570
算了 当我没说
It doesn't matter.

755
01:01:13,310 --> 01:01:16,370
63号 敌人从四面八方赶过去
63, confirm. We've got Skinnies moving in from all directions.

756
01:01:16,450 --> 01:01:18,350
我们要赶快支援他们
We need to get them help now.

757
01:01:19,490 --> 01:01:23,250
索马里人正赶往渥尔考特的坠机地点
Indigenous personnel advancing to Wolcott crash site.

758
01:01:24,560 --> 01:01:25,820
请重复
Say again. Over.

759
01:01:25,890 --> 01:01:28,190
一大堆人正蜂拥而上
A lot of people closing in.

760
01:01:30,500 --> 01:01:33,090
第四小队离那儿还有多远
How far is Chalk Four from the crash site?

761
01:01:33,330 --> 01:01:35,960
- 六个街口 - 他们要加快
- Six blocks, sir. - They need to haul ass.

762
01:02:30,320 --> 01:02:32,050
趴下 趴下
Get down! Get down!

763
01:02:33,360 --> 01:02:35,050
斯科特 你没事吧
Scotty, are you okay?

764
01:02:36,900 --> 01:02:38,360
别回去
No, don't go back!

765
01:02:48,270 --> 01:02:50,300
趴下 趴下
Get down! Get down!

766
01:02:52,650 --> 01:02:54,010
武装车
Technicals!

767
01:02:54,280 --> 01:02:55,540
看到了
Got them!

768
01:03:02,490 --> 01:03:04,720
六点钟方向 快走
Six o'clock! Move, move!

769
01:03:30,020 --> 01:03:31,810
快离开这儿
Come on. Get out of the way.

770
01:03:38,090 --> 01:03:40,080
快走
Go, go, go!

771
01:03:45,670 --> 01:03:46,860
快走
Go, go!

772
01:03:50,200 --> 01:03:51,430
快点
Come on!

773
01:03:59,850 --> 01:04:01,540
尤瑞克 快离开
Yurek, leaving!

774
01:04:04,850 --> 01:04:06,080
快点
Come on!

775
01:05:33,470 --> 01:05:37,100
U64号 左转 左转
Uniform 64, left turn. Left turn.

776
01:05:37,540 --> 01:05:41,340
R64号 你得告诉我该在哪条该死的街上才往左转
Romeo 64, I need to know before I get to the goddamn street!

777
01:05:41,710 --> 01:05:44,310
你得先停一下 消息发出时延迟
You have to slow down. There's a delay.

778
01:05:44,550 --> 01:05:49,150
侦察机的情报是先送到联合指挥中心 然后再转到我这儿
From the time directions are relayed from surveillance to JOC, then to me.

779
01:05:49,560 --> 01:05:52,390
我们不能停下来 我们正受到猛烈的攻击
We can't slow down! We're taking heavy enemy fire!

780
01:05:52,530 --> 01:05:54,250
我们不能停下来
We can't slow down!

781
01:05:54,330 --> 01:05:58,200
丹尼 我正在接收"奥利安"侦察机的情报
Danny, I'm getting information from Orion surveillance above.

782
01:05:54,410 --> 01:05:58,420
此次行动中有1架P3 Orion反潜预警机负责战场监控

783
01:05:58,260 --> 01:06:01,130
快告诉我该怎么到坠机地点
So get me my fucking directions to the crash site!

784
01:06:01,200 --> 01:06:05,230
丹尼 等一下 我这里看不清你的位置
Danny, hold on. I no longer have the best view of your route.

785
01:06:05,500 --> 01:06:08,100
那快赶去看得到的地方呀 该死的
Just get your ass in the right place, God damn it!

786
01:06:08,170 --> 01:06:11,300
现在史崔克的车队怎样了
What in the hell is the status of Struecker's humvees?

787
01:06:11,480 --> 01:06:14,310
勒尔上校 史崔克的车队还有多久会回到基地
Colonel Harrell, ETA to base, Struecker's column.

788
01:06:14,680 --> 01:06:16,740
就快到了
ETA to base momentarily.

789
01:06:24,190 --> 01:06:25,680
开门
Open the gate!

790
01:06:47,380 --> 01:06:49,970
- 把他抬下车 - 快
- Get him out! Let's go! Let's go! - Come on.

791
01:06:52,650 --> 01:06:54,080
小心他的头
Watch his head.

792
01:06:54,150 --> 01:06:55,520
小心
Easy.

793
01:07:03,560 --> 01:07:06,660
- 布莱克博德 你听到吗 - 快带他去治疗
- Blackburn. Blackburn, you hear me? - Get him to a medic.

794
01:07:40,800 --> 01:07:44,430
星41号正在坠机地点抢救伤者
Star 41 is at the crash site to evacuate the injured. Over.

795
01:07:44,500 --> 01:07:45,600
收到
Roger that.

796
01:08:24,740 --> 01:08:26,110
我来帮你
I got you.

797
01:08:26,680 --> 01:08:27,870
小心
Easy.

798
01:08:35,020 --> 01:08:36,890
杰利顿 你还行吧
Galentine, you all right?

799
01:08:37,090 --> 01:08:40,860
杰利顿 寇兹 跟我上 掩护火力
Galentine, Kurth, with me! Cover fire, now.

800
01:08:40,930 --> 01:08:42,150
全力掩护
Full cover!

801
01:08:55,810 --> 01:08:58,370
有几个人在里面
How many are in there?

802
01:08:58,440 --> 01:09:01,350
两名驾驶员死了 两名机工长受伤
Two pilots are dead, the two crew chiefs are wounded!

803
01:09:01,410 --> 01:09:03,540
他伤得很重 我们先把他救出来
This guy's hurt bad. We gotta get out of here now.

804
01:09:03,620 --> 01:09:05,080
好 去吧
All right. Go ahead.

805
01:09:37,250 --> 01:09:41,520
26号 26号 这里是25号 那辆武装车是你打的吗
26, 26, this is 25. Is that you shooting up the technicals? Over.

806
01:09:42,020 --> 01:09:43,610
26号收到
This is 26. Roger that.

807
01:09:43,820 --> 01:09:47,920
迪托马索 占领东南角 我们要建立起防线
DiTomasso, take the southeast corner. We're setting up a perimeter. Over.

808
01:09:48,030 --> 01:09:50,690
26号收到 马上过去
This is 26. Roger that. Moving there now.

809
01:09:50,830 --> 01:09:52,130
出发
Move out!

810
01:09:54,930 --> 01:09:56,990
斯蒂尔上尉 斯蒂尔上尉 请回答
Captain Steele. Captain Steele, come in.

811
01:09:58,900 --> 01:10:00,930
这里是64号 请说吧 25号
Go ahead, 25. This is 64.

812
01:10:01,170 --> 01:10:05,800
伤者两名 两名直升机驾驶员阵亡
We got two wounded and we got both the pilots dead in the chopper!

813
01:10:06,050 --> 01:10:07,770
这里需要医疗救援
We need a medivac over here now!

814
01:10:08,310 --> 01:10:13,270
25号告诉我那里在激烈交火 直升机没法降落 你要先守住防线
25 is telling me it's too hot to land a bird. You gotta secure the perimeter first. Over.

815
01:10:14,290 --> 01:10:15,480
悍马车队呢
Where are the humvees?

816
01:10:15,550 --> 01:10:18,520
25号 车队一定会到
Be advised, 25, the convoy will be there.

817
01:10:18,690 --> 01:10:21,820
他们正遭到猛烈攻击 64号呼叫完毕
They're encountering a lot of resistance. 64 out.

818
01:10:33,910 --> 01:10:37,600
- 快接手五零机枪 - 你很快就会看到前面的坠机地点了
- Get the 50 up! - You should see the crash directly ahead.

819
01:10:37,780 --> 01:10:39,570
我前面只看到路障
All I see is a roadblock!

820
01:10:41,380 --> 01:10:43,940
好吧 我另找一条路
All right, I'll have to figure out another way.

821
01:11:09,110 --> 01:11:12,130
快建立防线 把伤员载上车
Give me a defensive perimeter so we can load the wounded.

822
01:11:32,520 --> 01:11:34,220
奥西克 快开枪
Fire your weapon, Othic!

823
01:11:46,210 --> 01:11:49,000
跟我女儿说叫她们安心
Tell my girls I'll be okay.

824
01:11:55,080 --> 01:11:56,080
奥西克
Othic!

825
01:11:58,820 --> 01:11:59,980
军医
Medic!

826
01:12:31,120 --> 01:12:33,310
军医 军医
Medic! Medic!

827
01:12:33,720 --> 01:12:37,420
乔伊斯 快过来帮我把他抬起来
Joyce! Joyce! Come on, help me pick him up!

828
01:12:39,020 --> 01:12:43,090
快把我们带出这条该死的街道 坠机地点到底在哪里
Get us off this fucking street! Where's the crash site? Say again.

829
01:12:43,630 --> 01:12:46,390
直走两百米
Keep going straight 200 meters.

830
01:12:47,170 --> 01:12:48,290
收到
Roger that.

831
01:12:49,870 --> 01:12:51,170
走吧
Let's go!

832
01:12:51,640 --> 01:12:53,630
快走吧 该死的 走
Let's go, God damn it, let's go!

833
01:13:11,860 --> 01:13:14,050
嘿 汤布里 过来
Hey, Twombles. Come here.

834
01:13:18,660 --> 01:13:20,830
悍马不会回来了
The humvees ain't coming back, dude.

835
01:13:21,600 --> 01:13:22,690
什么
What?

836
01:13:24,070 --> 01:13:26,040
我们要去找他们吗
Were we supposed to go to them?

837
01:13:26,110 --> 01:13:28,200
我以为他们会来找我们呢
I thought they were supposed to come to us.

838
01:13:28,270 --> 01:13:29,370
可恶
Shit.

839
01:13:30,440 --> 01:13:32,970
- 我们想我们该去找他们了 - 可恶
- I think we're supposed to go to them. - Shit.

840
01:13:34,350 --> 01:13:37,440
好吧 我们去坠机地点
Okay, let's go to the crash site.

841
01:13:37,950 --> 01:13:38,950
好的
Okay.

842
01:13:39,020 --> 01:13:42,540
别在我耳边开枪 我都快聋了
Just don't fire that thing so close to my head. I can barely hear as it is.

843
01:13:42,620 --> 01:13:43,850
好 出发
Okay, move out.

844
01:13:56,700 --> 01:13:58,230
可恶 趴下
Shit! Get down!

845
01:14:00,470 --> 01:14:03,570
我才警告过你 别靠这么近打 如果你再这样…
What did I just tell you? I swear to God if you do that again...

846
01:14:03,640 --> 01:14:04,640
闭嘴
Shut up!

847
01:14:08,250 --> 01:14:10,270
尼尔森 你没事吧
You okay? Nelson.

848
01:14:10,720 --> 01:14:11,940
你没事吧
You all right?

849
01:14:12,020 --> 01:14:13,020
你说什么
What?

850
01:14:13,550 --> 01:14:16,950
搜救直升机正在现场展开救援
Search and rescue bird on station inserting medics.

851
01:14:28,400 --> 01:14:29,400
快上
Go!

852
01:14:34,210 --> 01:14:35,700
上 上
Go, go!

853
01:14:37,980 --> 01:14:41,640
该死的 C-2 这里是68号 我们被击中了
Son of a bitch. C-2, this is 68. We've been hit.

854
01:14:41,710 --> 01:14:45,310
超级68号 你的旋翼冒烟了
Super 68, there is smoke coming from the top of your rotor.

855
01:14:45,380 --> 01:14:47,750
- 建议你立刻返航 - 收到
- Advise you to come out now. - Roger.

856
01:14:47,820 --> 01:14:49,290
最后一个下去了
Dropping last man.

857
01:14:51,890 --> 01:14:55,880
阿特 我看到十二点钟方向有扛着RPG的人 你看得到吗
Art, I've got skinnies with RPGs at 12 o'clock. Can you see them?

858
01:14:55,960 --> 01:14:57,830
看到了 左转九十度
Got them. Give me 90 degrees left.

859
01:15:08,640 --> 01:15:09,940
68号现在退出战场
68 coming out.

860
01:15:11,840 --> 01:15:13,940
超级68号现在退出
Super 68 is out. Over.

861
01:15:24,190 --> 01:15:26,890
韦基 情况如何
Hey, Wilkie, what's the situation in there?

862
01:15:27,030 --> 01:15:28,860
驾驶员都死了
Both pilots are dead.

863
01:15:29,700 --> 01:15:32,630
25号 我们无法移动他们 马丁
25, we can't move these guys, Matty.

864
01:15:32,970 --> 01:15:34,930
如果我们勉强搬动他们会让他们没命的
We'll kill them just carrying them.

865
01:15:35,000 --> 01:15:37,030
- 就在这儿抢救 - 收到
- Stabilize in here? - Roger.

866
01:15:37,640 --> 01:15:40,760
就在直升机里抢救 重复 就在这儿抢救
Stabilize in the bird. Repeat: Stabilize in here. Over.

867
01:15:40,870 --> 01:15:43,000
收到了 韦基 我们替你们掩护
Understood, Wilkie. We got you covered. Over.

868
01:15:43,080 --> 01:15:46,640
超级64号 去接替渥尔考特（超级61号）的位置
Super 64, come inbound and take Wolcott's position.

869
01:15:47,480 --> 01:15:49,950
收到 64号进去了
Roger. 64 is inbound.

870
01:16:16,980 --> 01:16:18,570
超级64号 你没事吧
Super 64, you all right?

871
01:16:18,640 --> 01:16:21,440
这里是超级64号 我没事
This is Super 64. We're good.

872
01:16:21,650 --> 01:16:24,410
确定吗 你的机身看来受损了
You sure? You look like you got clipped pretty good.

873
01:16:24,750 --> 01:16:26,740
仪表板一切正常
Instrument panels are okay.

874
01:16:27,020 --> 01:16:31,120
我们没事 就是机身有点晃动 不过没事
No, we're good. Got a slight vibration in the pedals, but we're good.

875
01:16:31,690 --> 01:16:35,720
好吧 马上回机场降落 检查一下以策安全
All right, put her down on the airfield, 64. Have it checked out just to be safe.

876
01:16:36,530 --> 01:16:37,530
收到
Roger.

877
01:16:40,200 --> 01:16:44,640
机身晃动得很厉害 再检查一下系统
I'm getting a lot of movement in these pedals. Check the systems again.

878
01:16:59,790 --> 01:17:02,150
尾桨失效了
We lost the tail rotor! It's gone!

879
01:17:02,220 --> 01:17:03,850
64号正在坠落
64 is going down!

880
01:17:05,290 --> 01:17:07,050
64号正在坠落
64 is going in hard.

881
01:17:08,430 --> 01:17:09,920
64号正在坠落
64 going down.

882
01:17:15,000 --> 01:17:16,660
我们正在坠落
We're going down.

883
01:17:21,910 --> 01:17:23,810
快派史崔克的车队回去
Get Struecker's column back out there.

884
01:17:23,880 --> 01:17:26,170
叫他们赶到杜兰特的坠机地点
They need to get to Durant's crash site fast.

885
01:17:26,240 --> 01:17:29,080
- 又有一架直升机坠毁了 - 快去救他们
- Got another bird down. - I want them out of there.

886
01:17:29,510 --> 01:17:30,710
把他们都救出来
All of them.

887
01:17:31,720 --> 01:17:33,510
64完了
Super 64 is out.

888
01:17:33,590 --> 01:17:34,680
什么
What?

889
01:17:40,660 --> 01:17:42,650
他们是说另外一架黑鹰
They talking about another Hawk?

890
01:17:48,800 --> 01:17:52,130
斯蒂尔上尉 再不前进就会受困
Captain Steele, we got to move or we're gonna get pinned down!

891
01:17:52,200 --> 01:17:54,230
我们正在尽快前进
We're moving just as fast as we can.

892
01:17:54,310 --> 01:17:57,470
你别管我的队伍
You let me do my job and you do yours. Over.

893
01:18:05,220 --> 01:18:08,150
- 操 操 - 路兹 趴下
- Fuck! Fuck! - Ruiz, stay down.

894
01:18:08,220 --> 01:18:09,620
- 我就知道… - 军医
- I fucking knew... - Medic.

895
01:18:09,690 --> 01:18:13,680
去他的 斯蒂尔上尉 我来干掉那窗户的火力点
Fuck this! Captain Steele, I'll take out the threat in the window.

896
01:18:13,760 --> 01:18:16,100
我们在灰色大楼集合 就冲进去 上尉
We'll rally point the gray building. Coming through, Captain.

897
01:18:16,130 --> 01:18:17,130
什么
Sarg'nt!

898
01:18:17,200 --> 01:18:18,250
好 行动
All right, let's move!

899
01:18:18,330 --> 01:18:20,260
- 行动 快 - 行动 行动
- Let's move! Now! - Move! Move!

900
01:18:23,900 --> 01:18:25,200
掩护我
Cover me!

901
01:18:31,210 --> 01:18:33,640
- 走吧 行动 - 快离开
- Let's go, let's move! - Moving out.

902
01:18:39,580 --> 01:18:40,580
友军
Friendly!

903
01:18:40,650 --> 01:18:42,090
友军进来了
Friendlies coming through!

904
01:18:42,150 --> 01:18:44,350
走吧 快走
Let's go, let's go! Move up!

905
01:18:44,460 --> 01:18:46,360
快 快
Come on, come on!

906
01:18:46,790 --> 01:18:47,820
快
Come on!

907
01:18:55,700 --> 01:18:57,730
快走 走 快走
Move up! Go! Move up!

908
01:18:57,800 --> 01:18:59,430
你在干什么鬼东西
What the fuck are you doing out there?

909
01:18:59,500 --> 01:19:02,440
我在干我该干的 现在我们要赶到坠机地点
I'm doing my job! Now we got to get to that crash site!

910
01:19:02,510 --> 01:19:05,100
我们一定要赶到那条街 要马上行动起来
We got to get out on that street, and we got to move!

911
01:19:05,880 --> 01:19:07,970
而你也要跟上来
And you have got to keep up, sir!

912
01:19:08,080 --> 01:19:10,240
别对我下令 军士长
Don't you ever give me orders, Sergeant.

913
01:19:10,320 --> 01:19:13,110
我们没办法继续战斗 你知道吗
We are combat ineffective, you understand me?

914
01:19:13,250 --> 01:19:14,980
有太多的伤员了
We got too many dang wounded to move!

915
01:19:15,050 --> 01:19:18,650
那把你的一些人分给我 我带他们绕到坠机地点去
Then give me some of your shooters and I'll circle us to the bird.

916
01:19:20,990 --> 01:19:23,480
格里姆斯 你是第四小队的吧
Grimes! You're with Chalk Four?

917
01:19:23,660 --> 01:19:24,690
是的 长官
Yes, sir!

918
01:19:24,900 --> 01:19:28,330
好 那就跟着"三角洲" 到埃利斯曼中士那里归队
All right, hook up with Delta! Rejoin with Sergeant Eversmann.

919
01:19:28,900 --> 01:19:31,160
其他的人留守这里
The rest of you men, secure this position!

920
01:19:31,240 --> 01:19:33,470
照顾好伤员 我们在这里等车队来
Treat the wounded, we'll wait for the convoy!

921
01:19:33,540 --> 01:19:36,010
然后再去坠机地点会合
Then we'll rally at the crash site. Roger!

922
01:19:36,270 --> 01:19:37,670
大家听到了 出发
Come on, guys, let's go!

923
01:20:08,710 --> 01:20:11,800
C-2 我这里有两名"三角洲"的狙击手 舒加特和戈登…
C-2, I have two Delta snipers, Shughart and Gordon...

924
01:20:11,880 --> 01:20:14,570
自愿前往保护第二坠机地点
volunteering to secure crash site two. Over.

925
01:20:15,110 --> 01:20:19,520
不允许 超级62号 不能冒险再损失另一架直升机了
No, Super 62, negative that request. Can't risk another bird.

926
01:20:21,120 --> 01:20:25,180
我们看不清那里的情况 不确定是否有人生还
We don't see anything moving down there now, we don't even know if anyone's alive.

927
01:20:26,320 --> 01:20:29,050
地面部队正赶过去
A ground team is being organized to go in now.

928
01:20:29,130 --> 01:20:30,860
地面部队多久能赶到
ETA on ground team? Over.

929
01:20:31,130 --> 01:20:33,760
不清楚 但不用很长时间
Unknown, not long.

930
01:20:34,400 --> 01:20:36,300
你们尽力从空中协助
Do what you can from the air.

931
01:20:40,740 --> 01:20:42,500
来 大家过来集合
All right, gather around!

932
01:20:42,640 --> 01:20:45,910
杜兰特的64号坠毁了 我们现在要去救他
Durant's 64 is down. We're going back in to get him!

933
01:20:45,980 --> 01:20:48,070
你疯了 那里还有人生还吗
That's crazy. Is there anyone alive on that?

934
01:20:48,150 --> 01:20:50,710
这没关系 总之绝决不抛弃同袍
Doesn't matter, no one gets left behind. You know that.

935
01:20:50,780 --> 01:20:52,980
- 我们在浪费时间 - 好了
- We're wasting time here. - All right.

936
01:20:53,150 --> 01:20:56,180
好啦 五分钟内重新武装起来 多带弹药
Refit and max out ammo and grenades, you got five!

937
01:20:57,360 --> 01:20:59,380
西斯摩尔 你打算去什么鬼地方
Sizemore, where the hell do you think you're going?

938
01:20:59,460 --> 01:21:02,290
- 跟你们一起去 - 你还伤着 不能去
- With you guys. - Not with that cast on you're not.

939
01:21:03,030 --> 01:21:06,290
好啦 好啦 去拿头盔吧
All right, all right, all right. Go get your k-pot.

940
01:21:08,600 --> 01:21:09,790
你说句话呀
Talk to me.

941
01:21:09,970 --> 01:21:11,700
我不能再回去
I can't go back out there.

942
01:21:11,770 --> 01:21:16,230
托马斯 大家都跟你一样害怕
Thomas, everyone feels the same way you do. All right?

943
01:21:16,310 --> 01:21:19,570
所以你现在的表现才显得重要
It's what you do right now that makes a difference.

944
01:21:20,550 --> 01:21:21,840
你自己决定吧
It's your call.

945
01:21:47,310 --> 01:21:50,430
最好把悍马车上的血迹冲掉
It'll probably help to wash the blood out of the humvees.

946
01:21:59,920 --> 01:22:01,850
史崔克中士
Sergeant Struecker!

947
01:22:02,520 --> 01:22:06,220
史崔克中士 我能去吗
Sergeant Struecker! Can I go, Sarge?

948
01:22:06,290 --> 01:22:08,380
- 你带够弹药了吗 - 带够了 中士
- You got some ammo? - Roger that, Sarge!

949
01:22:08,460 --> 01:22:09,650
上车吧
Hop in!

950
01:22:27,980 --> 01:22:29,070
等等
Wait!

951
01:22:30,450 --> 01:22:32,210
来吧 托马斯 上车
Let's go, Thomas. Get in!

952
01:22:51,770 --> 01:22:53,760
尼尔森 汤布里 请回答 我是杰利顿
Nelson, Twombly, come in. This is Galentine.

953
01:22:53,840 --> 01:22:55,830
我们需要知道车队的位置
We need to position the convoy. Over.

954
01:22:56,140 --> 01:22:58,630
尼尔森 汤布里 请回答 我是杰利顿
Nelson, Twombly, come in. This is Galentine. Over.

955
01:22:58,710 --> 01:22:59,710
什么
What?

956
01:23:00,850 --> 01:23:03,140
- 你刚才说什么了吗 - 什么
- You said something. What? - What?

957
01:23:04,520 --> 01:23:05,520
好吧
Fine.

958
01:23:07,450 --> 01:23:09,680
呼叫不上 中士 我呼叫不上他们
I can't raise him, Sergeant, I can't raise him.

959
01:23:09,750 --> 01:23:11,950
中士 我们离开这鬼地方
Sergeant, let's get the fuck out of here and evac.

960
01:23:13,990 --> 01:23:15,220
- 离开这儿 - 好吧
- Let's move out. - All right!

961
01:23:15,290 --> 01:23:16,890
回到据点那儿
Back to the stronghold!

962
01:23:17,360 --> 01:23:18,360
走
Come on.

963
01:23:24,600 --> 01:23:25,760
走哪儿
Which way?

964
01:23:30,780 --> 01:23:33,770
- 我想是那儿吧 - 小声点儿
- That way, I think! - Not so fucking loud.

965
01:24:07,550 --> 01:24:08,940
乖驴子
Nice donkey.

966
01:24:27,270 --> 01:24:28,490
是游骑兵
Rangers?

967
01:24:29,230 --> 01:24:30,290
你谁呀
Who?

968
01:24:31,070 --> 01:24:34,000
我是尤瑞克 你这混蛋
It's Yurek! You fucking assholes!

969
01:24:34,940 --> 01:24:36,030
操
Fuck!

970
01:24:36,440 --> 01:24:38,930
该死的 我们差点儿就干掉你了
Dude, we almost fucking killed you!

971
01:24:39,080 --> 01:24:41,840
- 你快过来 - 操 你们过来这边
- Come to us! - Fuck you, come to me.

972
01:24:54,760 --> 01:24:56,090
对不起 中士
Sorry, Sarge!

973
01:24:56,160 --> 01:24:58,360
该死的 你刚才上哪儿了
Dude, where the fuck have you been?

974
01:24:58,430 --> 01:25:00,300
这不要紧 你带夜视镜了吗
Never mind, you brought NOD, right?

975
01:25:00,370 --> 01:25:02,630
我没带 你知道原因吗
No, I didn't bring it, and you want to know why?

976
01:25:02,700 --> 01:25:05,980
因为你说过 我们半小时就回来了 用不着那玩意儿
Because you said: "You're not gonna need that, dude, we'll be back in a half-hour."

977
01:25:06,040 --> 01:25:07,600
我不是这样跟你说的
No, I wasn't saying it to you.

978
01:25:07,670 --> 01:25:09,660
尼尔森 掩护这条路
Nelson, cover this way.

979
01:25:10,110 --> 01:25:11,630
我们需要夜视镜
Man, we're gonna need night vision.

980
01:25:11,710 --> 01:25:13,540
你有什么毛病
What's the matter with you?

981
01:25:14,550 --> 01:25:16,610
他聋了 是我的错
Oh, he's deaf. It's my fault.

982
01:25:17,480 --> 01:25:19,750
- 我们一定得离开这儿 - 那边
- We need to get out of here! - That way.

983
01:25:20,020 --> 01:25:22,990
我们不能离坠机地点太远 哪条路
We can't be far from the crash. Which way?

984
01:25:24,190 --> 01:25:26,180
我以为你知道
I thought you might know.

985
01:25:26,690 --> 01:25:28,220
出发吧
Let's move out.

986
01:25:37,640 --> 01:25:40,870
地面部队占据着马雷汉大街上的几栋建筑物
Ground forces have occupied several buildings along Marehan Road...

987
01:25:40,940 --> 01:25:42,630
但是都分散开来
but they're all spread out.

988
01:25:42,710 --> 01:25:47,270
埃利斯曼中士的第四小队在渥尔考特的坠机地点建立了防线
Eversmann's Chalk Four has set up a perimeter around Wolcott's crash site here.

989
01:25:47,380 --> 01:25:49,710
迪托马索在附近的大楼
DiTomasso is in the adjacent structure.

990
01:25:49,980 --> 01:25:54,010
斯蒂尔上尉率领着大约40名游骑兵 在这儿 在两个街口外
Captain Steele and about 40 men, Rangers, are here, a couple blocks away.

991
01:25:54,090 --> 01:25:55,610
他们的情况很惨
They're banged up pretty bad.

992
01:25:55,690 --> 01:26:00,180
他设立了伤亡聚集点 我想他们没办法继续前进了
He set up a casualty collection point, I don't think they're gonna be able to move.

993
01:26:00,860 --> 01:26:03,290
山德森军士和一小队"三角洲"…
Sergeant Sanderson and a small Delta team...

994
01:26:03,360 --> 01:26:07,320
由斯蒂尔上尉那儿出发 正赶往坠机地点
are moving from Steele's position to the crash site as we speak.

995
01:26:18,240 --> 01:26:19,400
吸引他们的火力
Draw off fire!

996
01:26:19,480 --> 01:26:22,540
等那些该死的家伙装弹时 就掩护我
When this asshole stops to reload, cover me!

997
01:26:22,650 --> 01:26:23,910
- 上 - 是
- Go! - Sir.

998
01:26:27,690 --> 01:26:28,690
再来一遍
Again!

999
01:26:33,560 --> 01:26:34,790
装弹
Loading!

1000
01:26:37,600 --> 01:26:39,220
继续 继续
Keep going! Keep going!

1001
01:26:39,730 --> 01:26:41,100
卡弹了
I'm jammed!

1002
01:26:42,600 --> 01:26:44,070
让我来
I got it!

1003
01:26:45,370 --> 01:26:46,800
该死的
No, shit!

1004
01:26:59,720 --> 01:27:01,120
RPG
RPG!

1005
01:27:15,930 --> 01:27:18,490
你还好吧 没事吧
You all right? You okay?

1006
01:27:18,670 --> 01:27:21,640
啊 我脑袋里好像在敲着钟
Yeah. I can hear bells ringing.

1007
01:27:23,240 --> 01:27:24,870
快 来吧
Come on! Come on!

1008
01:27:27,210 --> 01:27:28,210
走
Go!

1009
01:27:35,420 --> 01:27:38,360
距坠机地点六、七个街区外有一群人正在接近
There's a crowd advancing six, seven blocks from the crash.

1010
01:27:38,420 --> 01:27:40,790
舒加特和戈登再次请求…
Shughart and Gordon again request permission...

1011
01:27:40,860 --> 01:27:43,790
前往保护坠机地点 等车队到来
to secure until convoy arrives. Over.

1012
01:27:44,500 --> 01:27:47,560
将军 人群增加到好几百人
General, crowds are in the hundreds now.

1013
01:27:47,800 --> 01:27:51,260
他们看得会比我们清楚
From where they are, they can see things clearer than any of us.

1014
01:27:51,370 --> 01:27:53,270
他们很清楚自己的要求有多危险
They know what they're asking.

1015
01:27:53,470 --> 01:27:54,940
让我跟他们说
Let me talk to them.

1016
01:27:55,140 --> 01:27:56,230
这里是加里森
This is Garrison.

1017
01:27:56,310 --> 01:27:59,000
我要确定你们真的很清楚你们要求去干的事
I want to make sure that y'all understand what you're asking for...

1018
01:27:59,080 --> 01:28:01,050
请大声清楚地说出来
so say it out loud and clear.

1019
01:28:02,650 --> 01:28:06,450
我们要求到坠机地点建立防线并等待地面支援
We're asking to go in and set up a perimeter until ground support arrives.

1020
01:28:07,090 --> 01:28:11,250
你得清楚我无法告诉你要等多久 支援部队恐怕得花上好一阵子
And you realize that I cannot tell you when that might be, it could take a while.

1021
01:28:12,060 --> 01:28:14,420
- 明白 - 那你们还是要去
- Roger that. - You still want to go in there?

1022
01:28:14,690 --> 01:28:15,720
是的 长官
Yes, sir.

1023
01:28:19,730 --> 01:28:21,390
- 哈勒尔上校 - 是 将军
- Colonel Harrell? - Yes, General?

1024
01:28:21,470 --> 01:28:22,520
你来决定吧
It's your call.

1025
01:28:23,670 --> 01:28:25,030
明白
Roger that.

1026
01:28:26,940 --> 01:28:28,800
高夫纳（超级62号的机长） 把他们送过去
Goffena, put them in.

1027
01:28:43,050 --> 01:28:44,820
草泥马 草泥马
Motherfucker. Motherfucker.

1028
01:28:49,990 --> 01:28:51,050
RPG
RPG!

1029
01:29:01,010 --> 01:29:02,940
建立防线
Set up your perimeter!

1030
01:29:09,910 --> 01:29:11,910
这枚该死的火箭弹就插在他身上
There's a fucking rocket in him, sir!

1031
01:29:11,980 --> 01:29:15,980
奥西克 冷静点 该死的 它随时会爆炸 快走开
Othic, calm down, goddamn it! There's live ordnance, now get out!

1032
01:29:17,160 --> 01:29:18,650
这婊子养的
Son of a bitch.

1033
01:29:20,490 --> 01:29:23,650
来 把他抬起来 小心点 小心
All right, lift him up! Lift him up! Easy, easy!

1034
01:29:24,030 --> 01:29:28,190
好了 把他移进车里 很好 小心 小心
All right, get him in there! Good, good! Easy, easy!

1035
01:29:28,730 --> 01:29:30,220
快上车 开车
Get in that truck and drive.

1036
01:29:30,300 --> 01:29:32,020
- 我受伤了 上校 - 我们都受了伤
- But I'm shot, Colonel. - Everybody's shot.

1037
01:29:32,070 --> 01:29:34,060
我们得把犯人押回去
We need the prisoners! Let's go!

1038
01:29:35,240 --> 01:29:38,400
侦察机说你先开到哈瓦迪街再直走
Surveillance says to take Hawlwadig, then go straight.

1039
01:29:38,980 --> 01:29:43,240
麦肯奈特 你得掉头 回到哈瓦迪街
McKnight, we need you to turn around and head back to Hawlwadig.

1040
01:29:43,410 --> 01:29:45,880
你在糊弄我吗 我们才从那儿过来
You're shitting me! We just came through there!

1041
01:29:45,950 --> 01:29:47,650
肯定有更好的路线
