如果谁敢闯进来…
Anybody comes through that door...

1217
01:45:54,280 --> 01:45:56,840
先往他胸部打两枪 再往脑袋上打一枪
you give him two in the chest and one in the head.

1218
01:45:56,920 --> 01:46:00,320
- 明白了吗 - 我还能战斗 长官
- You understand? - I'm still in the fight, sir.

1219
01:46:00,620 --> 01:46:03,680
斯蒂尔上尉 我们这里有人需要救治
Captain Steele, I need a medivac in here now!

1220
01:46:03,760 --> 01:46:06,250
- 史密斯下士中弹了 - 等一下 25号
- Corporal Smith has been hit! - Hold on, 25.

1221
01:46:06,600 --> 01:46:08,030
我还可以打仗
Still in the fight.

1222
01:46:08,100 --> 01:46:09,580
斯蒂尔上尉 他伤得很重
Captain Steele, he's hurt pretty bad.

1223
01:46:09,630 --> 01:46:13,570
25号 我们这里也有很多伤员 你只能暂时在原地处理
25, we got wounded, too. You're just gonna have to maintain your situation, over.

1224
01:46:13,640 --> 01:46:16,200
如果半小时里不把他送进医院 就会没命了
If he doesn't get to a hospital in a half-hour, he's in trouble!

1225
01:46:16,710 --> 01:46:18,330
C-2 这里是64号
C-2, this is 64.

1226
01:46:18,580 --> 01:46:20,540
我们请求派遣医疗救援
I'm requesting an immediate medivac...

1227
01:46:20,610 --> 01:46:23,410
在第四小队那里有危重伤员
for a critically wounded at Chalk Four's location. Over.

1228
01:46:23,480 --> 01:46:26,350
指挥部 第四小队请求医疗救援
Command, Chalk Four is requesting medivac.

1229
01:46:26,450 --> 01:46:28,780
不能冒险 战况还很激烈
Can't risk it. It's still too hot.

1230
01:46:29,250 --> 01:46:34,120
上尉 我们不能派出医疗救援 请支持下去
Captain, we cannot send in medivac at this time. Sit tight. Over.

1231
01:46:34,460 --> 01:46:38,420
25号 这里是64号 无法派遣医疗救援 他们办不到
25, this is 64. It's a negative on the medivac. It's not possible.

1232
01:46:38,500 --> 01:46:42,260
联合指挥部不打算再派另一架直升机去冒险 你们要自己坚持下去
JOC cannot risk another bird. You're just gonna have to hold on.

1233
01:46:48,840 --> 01:46:50,270
好吧 我们自己来
All right. I got him.

1234
01:46:50,340 --> 01:46:52,770
直接压在伤口上
I want direct pressure on the wound.

1235
01:46:54,640 --> 01:46:57,110
你不会有事的 会好起来的
It's going to be all right. It's going to be okay.

1236
01:47:35,560 --> 01:47:38,930
这是我们的直升机

1237
01:47:41,020 --> 01:47:44,290
这里是K11号 我到了杜兰特的坠机地点
This is Kilo 11. I'm at the Durant crash site.

1238
01:47:44,360 --> 01:47:45,760
收到
Roger that.

1239
01:48:07,580 --> 01:48:09,780
第二坠机地点清除
Crash site two secured.

1240
01:48:09,850 --> 01:48:12,190
克里布斯中校找你 长官
Lieutenant Colonel Cribbs for you, sir.

1241
01:48:12,420 --> 01:48:13,450
克里布斯
Cribbs?

1242
01:48:13,530 --> 01:48:17,330
巴基斯坦体育场 第十山地师和联合国维和部队基地

1243
01:48:13,760 --> 01:48:17,020
- 长官 他们还在讨论路线 - 还要多久
- Sir, they're still debating the route. - How long?

1244
01:48:17,760 --> 01:48:19,390
还要好几个小时
At least a couple of hours.

1245
01:48:19,560 --> 01:48:21,220
我们等不了那么长的时间 乔
We haven't got that long, Joe.

1246
01:48:21,300 --> 01:48:25,890
巴基斯坦将军说我们事先没有通知他们这次行动
Pakistani General says, since we didn't deign to inform him of the raid...

1247
01:48:26,000 --> 01:48:29,940
而且把第十山地师和一百辆车发动起来要花点时间
it's gonna take some time to mobilize the 10th Mountain and 100 vehicles.

1248
01:48:30,010 --> 01:48:32,000
你告诉那个将军
You tell the general this:

1249
01:48:32,210 --> 01:48:35,370
我知道 但我也要提醒他
I understand, but it is my duty to remind him...

1250
01:48:35,450 --> 01:48:39,110
我的手下被武装民兵团团包围
that my men are surrounded by thousands of armed Somali militia.

1251
01:48:39,380 --> 01:48:44,380
我们必须立刻把他们救出敌对区域 送进安全区
It is imperative that we move them out of the hostile area and into the safe zone.

1252
01:48:45,060 --> 01:48:46,580
我现在就需要他的帮助
I need his help now.

1253
01:48:47,590 --> 01:48:48,820
是 长官
Yes, sir.

1254
01:48:53,930 --> 01:48:55,160
杜兰特
Durant.

1255
01:48:55,870 --> 01:48:57,800
迈克尔・杜兰特
Michael Durant.

1256
01:48:59,070 --> 01:49:00,130
是的
Yes.

1257
01:49:00,370 --> 01:49:02,770
你就是那些杀害我同胞的游骑兵
You are the Ranger who kills my people?

1258
01:49:03,140 --> 01:49:06,370
我不是游骑兵 我是飞行员
I'm not a Ranger. I'm a pilot.

1259
01:49:10,480 --> 01:49:11,950
那就对了
That's right.

1260
01:49:12,450 --> 01:49:14,970
美国人不抽烟了
None of you Americans smoke anymore.

1261
01:49:18,720 --> 01:49:22,520
你们都过着无趣的生活
You all live long, dull, uninteresting lives.

1262
01:49:25,230 --> 01:49:27,220
你为什么要抓我
What do you want with me?

1263
01:49:27,600 --> 01:49:29,570
你们手上有我们的人质
You have taken hostages.

1264
01:49:30,730 --> 01:49:32,130
我们手上有你
We have you.

1265
01:49:32,370 --> 01:49:35,200
美国政府才不会跟你谈判
My government will never negotiate for me.

1266
01:49:36,140 --> 01:49:40,510
那么我就跟你谈判吧
Then perhaps you and I can negotiate, huh?

1267
01:49:42,250 --> 01:49:44,080
我们都是军人
Soldier to soldier.

1268
01:49:50,890 --> 01:49:52,550
我作不了决定的
I'm not in charge.

1269
01:49:55,690 --> 01:49:59,530
当然不能 你有能力杀人 却没有能力谈判
Of course not. You have the power to kill, but not negotiate.

1270
01:50:00,630 --> 01:50:03,760
在索马里 杀人就是谈判
In Somalia, killing is negotiation.

1271
01:50:05,100 --> 01:50:08,300
你们真的以为你们抓到了艾迪德将军
Do you really think if you get General Aidid...

1272
01:50:08,810 --> 01:50:11,470
我们就会放下武器
we will simply put down our weapons...

1273
01:50:12,240 --> 01:50:14,540
接受美式民主
and adopt American democracy?

1274
01:50:15,650 --> 01:50:17,740
或是停止杀戮吗
That the killing will stop?

1275
01:50:17,880 --> 01:50:21,940
我只知道没有胜利就没有和平
We know this: Without victory, there can be no peace.

1276
01:50:22,690 --> 01:50:25,310
杀戮永远不会停止
There will always be killing, you see?

1277
01:50:25,690 --> 01:50:28,250
这就是我们的方式
This is how things are in our world.

1278
01:50:40,670 --> 01:50:43,610
迈克・杜兰特 我们不会抛弃你
Mike Durant, we won't leave you behind.

1279
01:50:46,480 --> 01:50:49,470
迈克・杜兰特 我们不会抛弃你
Mike Durant, we won't leave you behind.

1280
01:50:52,580 --> 01:50:55,380
换你来 用双手按住
You got to take over from me. Both hands.

1281
01:51:03,390 --> 01:51:06,360
伤口在股动脉 但是我看不到
It's the femoral artery, but I can't see it.

1282
01:51:06,830 --> 01:51:10,100
它一定缩进骨盆内了
Which means that it's retracted up into the pelvis.

1283
01:51:10,530 --> 01:51:14,830
我必须把伤口找出来 用止血钳把它夹住才能止血
Which means that I have to find it and clamp it. The only way to stop the bleeding.

1284
01:51:14,900 --> 01:51:16,570
但麻醉剂用完了
I got no more IV's.

1285
01:51:18,340 --> 01:51:21,170
所以我要你帮忙 好吗
So, I'm going to need you to assist. Okay?

1286
01:51:21,380 --> 01:51:22,740
好的
Yeah, yeah.

1287
01:51:23,880 --> 01:51:27,340
听好 杰米 我要做一件事 但会很痛的
Now listen, Jamie. I got to do something, it's going to hurt.

1288
01:51:27,420 --> 01:51:28,420
好吗
Okay?

1289
01:51:28,520 --> 01:51:32,050
你会很痛的 不过只有这样我才能救你
I got to cause you more pain, but I have to do it to help you.

1290
01:51:32,120 --> 01:51:33,650
你听懂了吗
All right, you understand?

1291
01:51:33,720 --> 01:51:36,060
- 吗啡呢 - 不能用
- Morphine. - I can't.

1292
01:51:36,130 --> 01:51:38,860
那会长时间降低你的心跳的
It'll lower your heart rate too far. I'm sorry.

1293
01:51:38,930 --> 01:51:41,490
汤布里 抓紧他的手
Twombly, why don't you take his hands there?

1294
01:51:45,640 --> 01:51:48,630
我要把伤口撑开 紧紧压住他的大腿
I need you to hold the wound open, keep pressure on the top of the leg.

1295
01:51:48,710 --> 01:51:51,040
尤瑞克 你也抓住一只脚 顺便帮我拿着手电筒
Yurek, you're gonna take the feet and a flashlight.

1296
01:51:51,110 --> 01:51:52,270
听我数数
On my count.

1297
01:51:52,340 --> 01:51:54,500
准备好了 杰米
All right, Jamie. All right.

1298
01:51:56,610 --> 01:51:58,510
一 二…
One. Two.

1299
01:51:59,580 --> 01:52:00,640
三
Three.

1300
01:52:08,360 --> 01:52:10,550
等等 好 找到了
Wait, wait. Okay. I feel it.

1301
01:52:11,260 --> 01:52:12,890
我找到了
I feel the pulse.

1302
01:52:14,360 --> 01:52:15,700
我找到了
I got it. I got it.

1303
01:52:15,770 --> 01:52:17,360
我找到了 我找到了
I got it, yeah. I got it.

1304
01:52:17,430 --> 01:52:19,300
- 我找到了 - 你找到什么
- I got it. - You got it?

1305
01:52:19,470 --> 01:52:20,600
钳住伤口了
Clamp?

1306
01:52:22,940 --> 01:52:24,300
我钳住了
I got it clamped.

1307
01:52:24,370 --> 01:52:25,570
- 坚持住 - 钳住它
- Hold it. - Got it.

1308
01:52:25,640 --> 01:52:26,900
这里 快抓住
Here, grab it.

1309
01:52:27,580 --> 01:52:29,310
- 撕开它 - 我找到了
- It's tearing. - I got it.

1310
01:52:29,550 --> 01:52:31,410
- 医生 它又缩回去了 - 抓住它
- Doc, it's going back in! - Hold it!

1311
01:52:31,480 --> 01:52:32,710
撕开了
It's tearing!

1312
01:52:33,050 --> 01:52:36,310
- 好 撑开伤口 - 撑开了
- Okay. Get out. Hold the wound. - Okay, I'm holding.

1313
01:52:37,490 --> 01:52:39,010
把手拿开
Move your hand.

1314
01:52:49,970 --> 01:52:51,060
怎么了
What?

1315
01:53:10,290 --> 01:53:11,450
治好了吗
Fix it?

1316
01:53:14,890 --> 01:53:17,190
是的 治好了
Yeah, yeah. We got it.

1317
01:53:32,980 --> 01:53:34,880
你在干什么
What the hell are you doing?

1318
01:53:34,940 --> 01:53:39,280
磨咖啡豆的关键是不能磨得太细 也不能太粗
It's all in the grind, Sarg'nt. Can't be too fine, can't be too coarse.

1319
01:53:39,620 --> 01:53:41,850
格里姆斯 你弄好了
Grimesy, you are squared away.

1320
01:53:58,600 --> 01:54:02,040
军士 来一杯热腾腾的咖啡吧
Sarg'nt, how would you like a nice hot cup of Joe?

1321
01:54:04,110 --> 01:54:05,730
黄金海岸口味的
Gold Coast blend.

1322
01:54:06,110 --> 01:54:09,100
坐下来 我看看你的伤口
Sit down. I want to take a look at that foot.

1323
01:54:09,610 --> 01:54:12,100
- 没什么大不了的 - 坐下吧
- No, it's not a problem. - Come on, come on.

1324
01:54:18,190 --> 01:54:21,390
- 他们从哪儿把你找来的 - 办公桌后面
- Where the hell did they find you? - Behind a desk.

1325
01:54:22,790 --> 01:54:25,520
是真的 我没开玩笑
No, really. What, you think I'm kidding?

1326
01:54:29,370 --> 01:54:31,330
- 有人受伤吗 - 没有
- Is anybody hit? - We're good!

1327
01:54:36,710 --> 01:54:37,900
你们没事吧
You all right?

1328
01:54:37,970 --> 01:54:38,970
没事
Yeah!

1329
01:54:39,140 --> 01:54:40,630
大家都没事吧
Is everybody all right?

1330
01:54:40,710 --> 01:54:41,730
没事
Yeah!

1331
01:54:55,490 --> 01:54:56,750
敌袭
Incoming!

1332
01:55:09,710 --> 01:55:11,700
继续开火 快点

1333
01:56:02,230 --> 01:56:04,460
迪托马索中弹 把他救出去
DiTomasso's hit! Pull him out!

1334
01:56:37,790 --> 01:56:39,520
游骑兵 这里是K11号
Ranger here. This is Kilo 11.

1335
01:56:39,600 --> 01:56:42,940
我们是第四小队 在坠机地点的东南角 你是谁
This is Chalk Four. We're at the southeast corner of the crash site. Who's this? Over.

1336
01:56:42,740 --> 01:56:45,740
这位绰号Hoot的三角洲队员全名是Norm Hooten

1337
01:56:42,970 --> 01:56:44,910
这里是胡特 我带了三名友军一起进来了
This is Hoot. I'm coming in with three friendlies.

1338
01:56:44,930 --> 01:56:46,630
我需要掩护火力
I need some cover and fire. Over.

1339
01:56:46,700 --> 01:56:49,640
收到 K11号 停止射击 三角洲要进来了
Roger that, Kilo 11 . Hold your fire! Deltas coming in.

1340
01:56:49,710 --> 01:56:51,730
停止射击 停止射击
Hold your fire! Hold your fire!

1341
01:56:56,310 --> 01:57:00,940
让地面部队用红外求生灯标出目标位置
Ground personnel will have to mark target positions with infrared strobes.

1342
01:57:01,650 --> 01:57:05,420
然后让AH-6"小鸟"整晚地扫射敌人
Get little birds on strafing runs and keep them going all night long.

1343
01:57:05,520 --> 01:57:07,790
如果我们控制不住那里的状况
If we don't hold back this city...

1344
01:57:08,490 --> 01:57:11,460
到明早就可能要准备上百口棺材了
we'll have a 100 caskets to fill by morning.

1345
01:57:11,560 --> 01:57:12,790
是 长官
Yes, sir.

1346
01:57:12,900 --> 01:57:15,590
哈勒尔上校 通知第一坠机地点的地面部队
Colonel Harrell, ground personnel at crash site one...

1347
01:57:15,670 --> 01:57:19,620
用红外求生灯把目标标出来 方便我们空袭
will have to mark the target with infrared strobes in preparation for air strike.

1348
01:57:20,300 --> 01:57:22,840
巴基斯坦体育场

1349
01:57:25,740 --> 01:57:26,970
麦肯奈特
McKnight.

1350
01:57:31,050 --> 01:57:34,640
第十山地师和联合国维和部队就够人了
Between the 10th Mountain and U.N., we got enough personnel, okay?

1351
01:57:35,790 --> 01:57:38,580
丹尼 你们不必再回去
Danny, you guys do not have to go back out again.

1352
01:57:51,540 --> 01:57:56,880
晚上11:23

1353
01:57:58,780 --> 01:58:01,710
我不能死在这儿
I can't die here, man.

1354
01:58:02,510 --> 01:58:05,850
你不会死的 懂吗 你不会死
You're not going to die, all right? You're not going to die.

1355
01:58:07,520 --> 01:58:08,980
对不起
I'm sorry.

1356
01:58:09,450 --> 01:58:11,820
你不必道歉
You don't have anything to be sorry for.

1357
01:58:12,620 --> 01:58:15,110
你救了汤布里 你做得很好
You saved Twombly. You did perfect.

1358
01:58:17,160 --> 01:58:18,790
汤布里 你没事吧
You okay, Twombs?

1359
01:58:19,230 --> 01:58:21,090
杰米 我没事
Yeah, I'm okay, Jamie.

1360
01:58:22,300 --> 01:58:24,460
你是个好军人
You did what you were trained to do.

1361
01:58:25,500 --> 01:58:27,370
你应该感到骄傲
You should be proud of that.

1362
01:58:30,310 --> 01:58:31,930
和自豪
Be proud of that.

1363
01:58:32,480 --> 01:58:34,340
- 埃文 - 在
- Ev? - Yeah.

1364
01:58:36,550 --> 01:58:37,880
帮我一个忙
Do me a favor.

1365
01:58:38,750 --> 01:58:39,870
嗯
Yeah.

1366
01:58:40,880 --> 01:58:44,680
跟我父母说 我今天很英勇
You tell my parents that I fought well today.

1367
01:58:45,960 --> 01:58:47,290
说我…
That l...

1368
01:58:49,160 --> 01:58:50,490
说我…
That l...

1369
01:58:53,360 --> 01:58:55,300
我尽力了
And that I fought hard.

1370
01:58:57,200 --> 01:58:59,670
你自己亲口对他们说吧
You're going to tell them yourself, okay?

1371
01:58:59,740 --> 01:59:01,260
知道吗
Do you hear me?

1372
01:59:02,970 --> 01:59:04,340
好吗
All right?

1373
01:59:06,040 --> 01:59:09,030
- 悍马车队来了吗 - 来了 杰米
- Are the humvees here? - They're coming, Jamie.

1374
01:59:09,550 --> 01:59:11,040
他们来了
They're coming.

1375
01:59:11,610 --> 01:59:13,880
你只要再撑一下
You just got to hang in there a little bit.

1376
01:59:13,950 --> 01:59:16,540
- 再多撑一下子 - 小意思
- You hold on for just a little bit. - I can.

1377
01:59:16,620 --> 01:59:17,780
我行的
I can.

1378
01:59:19,160 --> 01:59:20,620
没问题
It's nothing.

1379
01:59:21,860 --> 01:59:23,290
没问题
It's nothing.

1380
01:59:24,160 --> 01:59:25,460
没问题
It's nothing.

1381
01:59:25,530 --> 01:59:27,660
- 没问题 - 没问题
- It's nothing. - It's nothing.

1382
01:59:28,800 --> 01:59:30,030
没问题
Nothing.

1383
01:59:37,810 --> 01:59:39,070
可恶
Oh, shit.

1384
01:59:39,640 --> 01:59:41,170
压住伤口
Hold the wound.

1385
02:00:08,240 --> 02:00:09,300
医生
Doc.

1386
02:00:12,110 --> 02:00:13,170
医生
Doc.

1387
02:00:30,690 --> 02:00:32,020
行了
It's okay.

1388
02:00:58,250 --> 02:00:59,980
你在干嘛
What are you doing?

1389
02:01:03,230 --> 02:01:04,890
我们需要弹药
We need the ammo.

1390
02:01:13,340 --> 02:01:15,300
你已经尽了力
You did all you could here.

1391
02:01:15,370 --> 02:01:17,270
他们应该派医疗队来的
They should've sent a medivac.

1392
02:01:18,270 --> 02:01:22,110
它一定会被击落的 我们没法再防守一个坠机地点
Right now we'd be out there defending another crashed chopper.

1393
02:01:22,210 --> 02:01:24,300
会有更多的人受伤
More men would get torn up.

1394
02:01:27,620 --> 02:01:28,780
也许吧
Maybe.

1395
02:01:29,450 --> 02:01:31,580
别想那么多
See, you're thinking. Don't.

1396
02:01:32,560 --> 02:01:35,720
中士 你不能决定让谁来受伤
Because, Sergeant, you can't control who gets hit or who doesn't.

1397
02:01:35,790 --> 02:01:38,260
或是谁从直升机上摔落
Who falls out of a chopper or why.

1398
02:01:38,490 --> 02:01:40,930
这就是战争 你也无能为力
It ain't up to you. It's just war.

1399
02:01:43,130 --> 02:01:45,430
是的 但史密斯还是死了
Yeah, well, Smith's still dead.

1400
02:01:46,600 --> 02:01:49,210
都是因为布莱克博德摔下来 然后才发生那么多事
If Blackburn wouldn't have fallen, none of this would have happened.

1401
02:01:49,240 --> 02:01:51,500
你想这么多也没用
Should have or could have, it don't matter.

1402
02:01:51,570 --> 02:01:55,340
以后你有的是时间去想
You'll get plenty of time to think about all that later. Believe me.

1403
02:01:59,220 --> 02:02:01,780
中士 你把弟兄们带到这儿
Sergeant, you got your men this far.

1404
02:02:03,090 --> 02:02:04,920
你已经尽了全力
You did it right today.

1405
02:02:04,990 --> 02:02:08,420
现在你要想该怎么把他们带出去了
You need to start thinking about getting these men out of here.

1406
02:02:14,860 --> 02:02:16,890
可以走了吗
Well, shall we?

1407
02:02:25,640 --> 02:02:28,170
我要四个人守住这角落
I need four guys in this corner now!

1408
02:02:34,780 --> 02:02:35,840
RPG
RPG!

1409
02:02:40,160 --> 02:02:42,750
这里是巴伯52号 准备好扫射了
This is Barber 52 in position for gun run.

1410
02:02:42,830 --> 02:02:44,950
老天爷 你看看
Jesus Christ. Look at that.

1411
02:02:45,930 --> 02:02:49,060
这里是25号 我看到了 你就在我上方
This is 25! I can see you. You're right above me.

1412
02:02:49,130 --> 02:02:52,570
埃利斯曼 我分不清敌友了 这里太混乱了
Eversmann, I can't tell who's who down there. Too much activity.

1413
02:02:52,640 --> 02:02:55,130
我会用红外求生灯把目标标示出来
I'll mark the target with a strobe! Over.

1414
02:02:55,370 --> 02:02:56,530
收到
Roger that.

1415
02:03:07,880 --> 02:03:09,250
看到了吗
You see it?

1416
02:03:11,820 --> 02:03:13,410
不 我什么都看不到
Nah, I can't see shit.

1417
02:03:14,320 --> 02:03:17,260
- 我要丢到屋顶 - 得有人帮你才行
- I'm putting it on the roof. - You're going to need some help!

1418
02:03:17,330 --> 02:03:18,330
掩护我
Cover me.

1419
02:03:19,530 --> 02:03:23,290
好 大家听我数到三 就开枪掩护他
Okay, guys, we're going to lay down some cover fire for him on three!

1420
02:03:23,500 --> 02:03:24,500
准备好了
Ready?

1421
02:03:24,670 --> 02:03:25,670
一
One.

1422
02:03:25,740 --> 02:03:26,830
二
Two.

1423
02:03:27,000 --> 02:03:28,730
三 上
Three. Go!

1424
02:04:01,300 --> 02:04:04,300
我看到目标了 准备进行扫射
I got your position. I got the target. We're inbound and hot.

1425
02:04:34,140 --> 02:04:36,500
把头低下 我们再扫射一圈
Y'all keep your heads down. We're coming back around.

1426
02:04:36,570 --> 02:04:37,630
收到了 C-4
Copy that, C-4.

1427
02:04:37,710 --> 02:04:42,410
C-2 这里是64号 车队在哪 我们还呆在这鬼地方
C-2, this is 64. Where the hell is the convoy? We're getting fucked here. Over.

1428
02:04:42,610 --> 02:04:45,940
在半路上 你们继续坚守阵地
You're half a click from your location. Hang in there.

1429
02:04:50,350 --> 02:04:51,440
可恶
Shit!

1430
02:05:04,270 --> 02:05:08,700
C-2 弹药扫光了 请求返回基地补充
C-2, miniguns dry. Request permission to return to base. Rearm. Over.

1431
02:05:08,770 --> 02:05:11,760
收到 第二队接入 进入火力支援区
Roger that. Second team inbound. Your station.

1432
02:05:12,010 --> 02:05:14,200
四分钟后进入攻击位置
On your location, four minutes.

1433
02:05:22,280 --> 02:05:24,550
他们来了 把伤员运上去
All right, they're here. Get the wounded ready to move.

1434
02:05:24,620 --> 02:05:25,780
快 快
Move! Move!

1435
02:05:25,860 --> 02:05:27,880
趴好 掩护我们
Lay down some cover fire!

1436
02:05:30,630 --> 02:05:32,120
我早就听到你们了
I thought I heard a noise out here!

1437
02:05:32,190 --> 02:05:34,440
让你的人上车 我们离开这鬼地方
Get your men loaded up. We're getting the hell out of here.

1438
02:05:34,460 --> 02:05:35,490
是 长官
Yes, sir.

1439
02:05:38,130 --> 02:05:40,900
25号 这里是64号 营救纵队已经到我们这儿了
25, this is 64. The rescue column has arrived.

1440
02:05:40,970 --> 02:05:43,400
大约五分钟后到你们那儿
Will be at your location in about 5 minutes.

1441
02:05:43,470 --> 02:05:45,440
让你的人做好撤退准备
Prepare your men for exfil, Sarg'nt.

1442
02:05:45,510 --> 02:05:47,640
收到 长官 收到了
Yeah, roger that, sir! Roger that!

1443
02:05:48,480 --> 02:05:52,240
五分钟 车队五分钟后就到
Five minutes! The convoy is going to be here in five minutes!

1444
02:06:12,330 --> 02:06:14,600
我要弹匣 埃利斯曼 我的弹药用完了
I need a mag! Eversmann, I'm out!

1445
02:06:14,700 --> 02:06:16,300
最后一个了
Here! It's my last one!

1446
02:06:21,380 --> 02:06:25,380
凌晨2:05

1447
02:06:26,280 --> 02:06:28,010
车队来了
The convoy is here!

1448
02:06:46,840 --> 02:06:50,360
埃利斯曼中士 听说你们要搭便车
Sergeant Eversmann. I heard you guys needed a lift!

1449
02:06:50,740 --> 02:06:52,000
是的 长官
Yes, sir!

1450
02:06:52,110 --> 02:06:55,080
把伤员抬上来
Bring your wounded right over there and start loading them up!

1451
02:07:02,280 --> 02:07:04,410
来 我来扶你
Hey, I got you. I got you.

1452
02:07:04,620 --> 02:07:06,820
没关系 我想走走
It's okay. I want to walk.

1453
02:07:07,890 --> 02:07:10,320
我也一样 走吧
Yeah, I would, too. Let's go!

1454
02:07:20,200 --> 02:07:21,530
走 快走
Move! Move!

1455
02:07:24,510 --> 02:07:28,100
我们把驾驶员的尸体拉出来就回体育场
We get the pilots' bodies out, and then we go to the stadium.

1456
02:07:28,380 --> 02:07:30,110
车上没有地方了
We're running out of room around here.

1457
02:07:30,180 --> 02:07:32,980
尽量挤一挤
Just gonna have to cram into every possible space.

1458
02:07:33,180 --> 02:07:38,180
第十山地师用装甲车保护我们从交战区撤退
Okay, 10th Mountain provides security for armor, walks us out of the hot zone.

1459
02:07:38,390 --> 02:07:39,880
第十山地师 不
10th Mountain? No.

1460
02:07:40,090 --> 02:07:43,180
我们游骑兵就可以殿后
Sir, with respect, my Rangers can provide rear security.

1461
02:07:43,290 --> 02:07:47,460
我们走出交战区再坐车
We'll walk you out of the hot zone, then we'll jump on the last few vehicles.

1462
02:07:48,260 --> 02:07:49,790
好 出发吧
Okay, let's get out of here.

1463
02:07:49,870 --> 02:07:51,200
出发
Let's go.

1464
02:07:51,270 --> 02:07:53,760
来吧
- All right, you got him? - Yeah, come on.

1465
02:07:55,700 --> 02:07:56,930
开车呀
Come on!

1466
02:07:58,140 --> 02:08:01,540
我们现在就在吸引子弹 快走吧
These things are fucking bullet magnets. Come on, let's go!

1467
02:08:01,610 --> 02:08:04,100
我们接到命令才能走 士兵
We go when I'm ordered to, soldier.

1468
02:08:06,580 --> 02:08:07,780
小心点
Careful.

1469
02:08:08,380 --> 02:08:10,050
小心 小心
Easy. Go easy.

1470
02:08:13,990 --> 02:08:15,080
小心
Easy.

1471
02:08:25,870 --> 02:08:28,100
上校 怎么回事
Colonel, what is going on down there?

1472
02:08:28,170 --> 02:08:31,370
他们要绕着尸体来拆开驾驶舱
They're dismantling the entire cockpit around the body.

1473
02:08:31,570 --> 02:08:35,240
还要多久 实话实说
How long is it going to take? I need an honest, no-shit assessment.

1474
02:08:36,180 --> 02:08:37,540
说不准
They can't say!

1475
02:08:39,520 --> 02:08:40,740
丹尼
Danny...

1476
02:08:42,250 --> 02:08:44,050
绝对不能抛弃同袍
no one gets left behind.

1477
02:08:44,750 --> 02:08:46,650
你明白吗
You understand me, son?

1478
02:08:47,060 --> 02:08:48,520
明白 将军
Yes, General.

1479
02:08:49,390 --> 02:08:51,020
该怎么做就怎么做
You do what you have to do.

1480
02:08:52,190 --> 02:08:53,350
收到
Roger.

1481
02:09:03,010 --> 02:09:05,500
- 还要多久 - 45分钟
- How much longer? - Forty-five minutes.

1482
02:09:05,940 --> 02:09:08,410
- 我们等不了45分钟 - 什么
- We don't have 45 minutes. - What?

1483
02:09:09,450 --> 02:09:13,640
我们等不了45分钟 懂吗
We don't have 45 minutes. Do you understand?

1484
02:09:15,220 --> 02:09:16,840
明白吗
Do you understand?

1485
02:09:18,450 --> 02:09:19,550
好吧
Okay.

1486
02:09:19,920 --> 02:09:22,820
- 快 把他抬出来 - 好了
- All right, come on. Bring him through. - I got him.

1487
02:09:23,360 --> 02:09:26,520
- 把伤员都救出来 - 来了
- Get all of his gear. Get the wounded out. - Got you, sir!

1488
02:09:26,800 --> 02:09:31,600
10月4日 星期一 早上5:45

1489
02:09:31,830 --> 02:09:33,960
- 快 快 快 - 来了
- Go! Move! - Got you!

1490
02:09:34,300 --> 02:09:36,330
快走 快走
Move out! Move out! Let's go!

1491
02:09:46,250 --> 02:09:47,340
操
Fuck!

1492
02:09:50,120 --> 02:09:51,280
要炸了
Fire in the hole!

1493
02:09:51,350 --> 02:09:53,250
- 走吧 快走 - 走
- Let's go! Move! - Let's go! Let's go!

1494
02:10:09,440 --> 02:10:12,840
- 开舱门 让我们进去 - 挤不下了 坐车顶吧
- Open up the hatch! We got men back here! - No room here! Go on the roof!

1495
02:10:12,910 --> 02:10:14,000
怎么回事
What's going on?

1496
02:10:14,080 --> 02:10:17,140
- 车顶 - 我才不坐车顶
- The roof? - I'm not getting on no fucking roof!

1497
02:10:18,050 --> 02:10:19,450
没地方坐了
No, no, it's full.

1498
02:10:20,520 --> 02:10:23,710
跑吧 继续前进 用车子作掩护
We're running out. Keep moving. Use the vehicles as cover.

1499
02:10:26,560 --> 02:10:28,220
走吧 出发
Move it! Let's go!

1500
02:10:45,540 --> 02:10:47,980
等一下 等一下
All right, hold it up. Hold it up.

1501
02:10:50,080 --> 02:10:51,600
- 快走 - 快走
- Move! - Go! Move!

1502
02:10:51,680 --> 02:10:52,700
快
Go!

1503
02:11:47,640 --> 02:11:49,660
趴下 趴下
Get down! Get down!

1504
02:11:51,310 --> 02:11:52,830
快趴下
Get down, lady!

1505
02:11:55,310 --> 02:11:56,680
我没子弹了
I'm out of ammo!

1506
02:11:57,510 --> 02:11:59,610
山德森 我没子弹了
Sanderson, I'm out of ammo!

1507
02:12:04,990 --> 02:12:06,580
别拿枪
Don't you do it.

1508
02:12:07,020 --> 02:12:09,510
- 你在干嘛 - 别去拿枪
- What are you doing? - Don't you damn do it.

1509
02:12:11,160 --> 02:12:12,750
库尔特 走吧
Kurth, let's go!

1510
02:14:36,540 --> 02:14:38,030
小心 小心
Easy. Easy.

1511
02:15:38,470 --> 02:15:40,230
啊 该死的
Ah, shit.

1512
02:15:40,300 --> 02:15:43,930
子弹错过你的颈静脉了 别动
Bullet missed your jugular by about three millimeters. Don't move.

1513
02:15:50,450 --> 02:15:52,240
下次看准点 走吧
Aim later. Go!

1514
02:15:53,380 --> 02:15:54,410
走
Go!

1515
02:15:58,420 --> 02:16:00,150
动作快点
Hurry up, hurry up.

1516
02:16:02,720 --> 02:16:06,680
嘿 别让他自个儿爬 帮帮他
Hey, don't let that man crawl. Somebody help that man.

1517
02:16:06,900 --> 02:16:08,390
帮帮他
Help him.

1518
02:16:11,200 --> 02:16:13,500
格里姆斯 干得好
Grimes, you did good.

1519
02:16:36,020 --> 02:16:37,290
该死
Oh, shit!

1520
02:17:08,290 --> 02:17:10,090
浴场在哪儿 少校
Where are the baths, Major?

1521
02:17:10,160 --> 02:17:11,850
从这儿过去就是 上尉
They're through there, Captain.

1522
02:17:37,620 --> 02:17:38,710
路兹
Ruiz.

1523
02:17:40,020 --> 02:17:42,550
嘿 中士
Hey, Sarg'nt. Hey.

1524
02:17:46,230 --> 02:17:47,390
上尉
Captain.

1525
02:17:47,460 --> 02:17:49,990
洛伦佐 你还好吧
Lorenzo. How you doing?

1526
02:17:52,870 --> 02:17:57,600
子弹擦过去 军医说我过两天就好了
It went in and out, so the medic said I should be okay in a couple of days.

1527
02:17:57,910 --> 02:17:59,570
真是好消息
That's great news.

1528
02:18:00,380 --> 02:18:01,770
我们要回去吗
We're going after them?

1529
02:18:01,840 --> 02:18:04,740
当然了 不过我们得先重整队伍
You bet your ass we will. We got to regroup.

1530
02:18:06,250 --> 02:18:08,220
别把我留下来
Don't go out without me.

1531
02:18:09,220 --> 02:18:11,980
别丢下我就回去
Don't go back out there without me.

1532
02:18:13,590 --> 02:18:15,450
我还能打仗
I can still do my job.

1533
02:18:17,190 --> 02:18:19,320
好好休息吧
You get some rest now, okay?

1534
02:18:21,260 --> 02:18:22,420
格里姆斯
Grimes.

1535
02:18:24,070 --> 02:18:27,630
没咖啡 我给你倒点茶吧
Little short on coffee, but I got you some tea.

1536
02:18:32,270 --> 02:18:33,900
还好吗 士兵
How you doing, soldier?

1537
02:18:35,080 --> 02:18:36,810
没感觉了
Can't feel a thing.

1538
02:18:53,130 --> 02:18:54,930
你要回去
You're going back in?

1539
02:18:56,500 --> 02:18:58,730
在那里还有弟兄
There are still men out there.

1540
02:19:00,800 --> 02:19:02,060
该死
God damn.

1541
02:19:07,480 --> 02:19:09,100
我每次回家
When I go home...

1542
02:19:09,840 --> 02:19:11,370
他们都问我
and people ask me:

1543
02:19:11,450 --> 02:19:14,110
胡特 你为什么从军
"Hey, Hoot, why do you do it, man?"

1544
02:19:15,380 --> 02:19:19,010
难道你是打仗打上瘾了吗
"Why? You some kind of war junkie?"

1545
02:19:20,020 --> 02:19:22,110
我一句话也说不出来
I won't say a goddamn word.

1546
02:19:22,760 --> 02:19:23,850
为什么
Why?

1547
02:19:24,860 --> 02:19:26,720
他们不会懂
They won't understand.

1548
02:19:28,260 --> 02:19:30,750
他们不懂我们干嘛要打仗
They won't understand why we do it.

1549
02:19:32,000 --> 02:19:35,370
我们是为了袍泽而拼命
They won't understand it's about the men next to you.

1550
02:19:37,940 --> 02:19:39,430
就这么简单
And that's it.

1551
02:19:41,380 --> 02:19:43,000
很简单
That's all it is.

1552
02:19:51,890 --> 02:19:56,820
想都别想 我习惯单枪匹马
Hey, don't even think about it, all right? I'm better on my own.

1553
02:20:01,860 --> 02:20:04,960
星期一 又是一周的开始
Hey, we started a whole new week. It's Monday.

1554
02:20:18,710 --> 02:20:20,680
过几天 布莱克博德问我
I was talking to Blackburn the other day...

1555
02:20:20,750 --> 02:20:24,880
什么改变了 我们为什么要回家
and he asked me, "What changed? Why are we going home?"

1556
02:20:26,990 --> 02:20:28,850
我说什么都没变
And I said, "Nothing."

1557
02:20:29,520 --> 02:20:33,260
但这不是实话 我想 一切都变了
But that's not true, you know. I think everything's changed.

1558
02:20:35,000 --> 02:20:36,490
我也变了
I know I've changed.

1559
02:20:42,270 --> 02:20:45,000
曾经有一个朋友问我
A friend of mine asked me before I got here...

1560
02:20:45,070 --> 02:20:47,300
那是在我们被派来这儿之前
It was when we were all shipping out.

1561
02:20:47,380 --> 02:20:48,770
他问我
He asked me:

1562
02:20:50,210 --> 02:20:53,340
你为什么要去打别人的仗
"Why are you going to fight somebody else's war?"

1563
02:20:53,750 --> 02:20:56,340
你自以为是英雄吗
"What, do y'all think you're heroes?"

1564
02:20:59,120 --> 02:21:01,850
当时我不知道该说什么
I didn't know what to say at the time...

1565
02:21:04,430 --> 02:21:07,020
现在我的答案是 不
but if he asked me again, I'd say no.

1566
02:21:09,430 --> 02:21:11,760
我不想当英雄
I'd say there's no way in hell.

1567
02:21:12,530 --> 02:21:14,560
没有人想当英雄
Nobody asks to be a hero.

1568
02:21:19,910 --> 02:21:22,170
只是时势造英雄
It just sometimes turns out that way.

1569
02:21:26,180 --> 02:21:29,640
回家后 我会去找你的父母
I'm gonna talk to your ma and pa when I get home, okay?

1570
02:22:32,500 --> 02:22:34,200
一千多名索马里人死亡

1571
02:22:34,300 --> 02:22:35,700
十九名美军阵亡

1572
02:22:36,320 --> 02:22:40,010
我的爱 你会坚强地活下去
My love, you are strong and you will do well in life.

1573
02:22:42,190 --> 02:22:44,660
我爱你和我的孩子
I love you and my children deeply.

1574
02:22:45,560 --> 02:22:48,760
每一天都会茁壮成长
Today and tomorrow, let each day grow and grow.

1575
02:22:50,300 --> 02:22:54,460
保持笑容 千万别被困境打倒
Keep smiling and never give up, even when things get you down.

1576
02:22:55,770 --> 02:22:58,200
最后 我的爱
So, in closing, my love...

1577
02:22:58,570 --> 02:23:02,410
今晚替我哄我的孩子入睡
tonight, tuck my children in bed warmly.

1578
02:23:02,840 --> 02:23:06,750
跟他们说我爱他们 替我拥抱他们…
Tell them I love them. Then hug them for me...

1579
02:23:07,650 --> 02:23:10,020
替爸爸亲吻他们 给他们道晚安
and give them both a kiss good night for Daddy.

